      <div class="pf-faq">
        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-green">ECO4</span>&nbsp; Can I get a free boiler in St Helens?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>Possibly yes. If you receive Universal Credit, Pension Credit, Child Tax Credit, Housing Benefit or other qualifying benefits, you may qualify for a fully funded boiler replacement under the ECO4 scheme. St Helens has a high proportion of ECO4-eligible households, particularly across WA10 and WA9. We assess eligibility free of charge at every survey. See <a href="https://www.gov.uk/apply-great-british-insulation-scheme" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gov.uk</a> for scheme details.</p></div></details>
        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-orange">BACK BOILER</span>&nbsp; Can you replace my back boiler in St Helens?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>Yes. Back boiler replacement is one of our most common St Helens jobs. The process involves removing the gas fire and surround, safely disconnecting the back boiler, capping the old flue, determining the best new boiler position and replumbing to it. For WA10 Victorian terraces this typically takes two days. We survey every back boiler property in person before quoting because the variation between properties is too great for remote estimates. Prices start from £2,500.</p></div></details>
        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-navy">COST</span>&nbsp; How much does a new boiler cost in St Helens?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>A like-for-like combi boiler installation starts from £1,800 fully fitted. System boilers from £2,200. Back boiler replacements from £2,500 depending on complexity. All prices include the boiler, installation, controls, magnetic filter, system flush, Benchmark and Gas Safe certificates. Written fixed-price quote after the free survey. Some households qualify for free installation under ECO4.</p></div></details>
        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-orange">TIME</span>&nbsp; How long does a boiler installation take in St Helens?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>A like-for-like combi replacement takes 4 to 6 hours in one day. A system boiler with new cylinder takes 1 to 2 days. A back boiler replacement including fire surround removal and replumb takes 1 to 2 days. We confirm the exact duration at the free survey.</p></div></details>
        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-green">GAS SAFE</span>&nbsp; Are you Gas Safe registered for St Helens boiler work?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>Yes. All our engineers are Gas Safe registered. Verify at <a href="https://www.gassaferegister.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gassaferegister.co.uk</a>. It is illegal to install a gas boiler without this registration. Gas Safe and Benchmark certificates issued on installation day for every job.</p></div></details>
        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-navy">LANDLORDS</span>&nbsp; Can you fit boilers in my St Helens rental properties?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>Yes. We install new boilers in St Helens rental properties and provide all required documentation. CP12 gas safety certificates issued on the day. We work with individual landlords and letting agents across WA10, WA11 and WA12. Portfolio landlords can request consolidated invoicing and annual compliance scheduling.</p></div></details>
        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-orange">WARRANTY</span>&nbsp; What warranty does a new boiler carry?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>Worcester Bosch and Vaillant offer up to 10-year warranties when installed by an accredited engineer and serviced annually. Ideal and Baxi offer between 5 and 10 years depending on the model. All our installations carry a 12-month workmanship guarantee. We register the manufacturer warranty on installation day. Annual servicing is required to keep the warranty valid, see our <a href="/boiler-service-st-helens">boiler service St Helens page</a>.</p></div></details>
